      • SHIFT_1

        public static final XOR32ShiftRandom.Shift SHIFT_1
        Shift strategy number one. 
        
 int shift(int x, final Param param) {
     x ^= x << param.a;
     x ^= x >>> param.b;
     return x^x << param.c;
 }
